{"tid":338591,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"假MK真毒撚去船P嘅後果","createTime":"2017-07-28T10:02:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-28T11:14:23.000Z","uid":58851,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"09d50f48b021eed60fc1795a4c13c012db265d3f","tid":338591,"uid":58851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T10:02:37.000Z","msg":"【17:15】約1個半小時後，蛙人在水底將青年救起，他昏迷由直升機送院搶救。<br />\n<br />\n船P男玩瀡滑梯疑失蹤，警方消防大搜索。下午近3時，一批男女趁周末前夕，乘遊艇出海遊玩，並在西貢大蛇灣對開海面停泊。期間船上一名19歲青年，在船尾玩瀡滑梯落水後不知所終，懷疑遇溺沉下海底，同行姓鄧男友人慌忙報警求助。水警輪及消防蛙人正在現場海面搜索。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170728/bkn-20170728151526374-0728_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170728%2Fbkn-20170728151526374-0728_00822_001.html&d=WB9wSc5z1ZO9upoRyOJmuYzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=b0bd7692\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170728/bkn-20170728151526374-0728_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"c058a3f7afef190625483128fc8b48c7b5f6adee","tid":338591,"uid":4826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T11:12:37.000Z","msg":"釘左rip"},{"pid":"2d43ad8a307f078f454f618a9a40abbc7ae8d319","tid":338591,"uid":28031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T11:14:23.000Z","msg":"沉左落海都冇人知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}